title: Understanding Cell Insertion and Deletion
text: Think about the different types of cells and structures you can manipulate in a worksheet. Consider individual cells, groups of cells, and larger structures.

title: Types of Cells in a Worksheet
text: In a worksheet, you can work with individual cells, rows, columns, and even entire worksheets. Consider how these can be inserted or deleted.

title: Exploring Options for Cell Manipulation
text: Which of the following options includes all possible types of cells and structures you can insert or delete in a worksheet?
choices: a range of cells, rows, and individual cells
a range of cells, rows, and individual cells, and entire worksheets
